reet by local representative, transfer to hotel. DAY 02 4 Island Tour by Long Tail Boat (B/L) After breakfast at hotel, proceed to 4 island tour. The Trip Our traditional longtail boat will take you out to explore some of the deserted tropical Islands in the Andaman Sea such as :- 1st stop Railey Beach: Secluded peninsular, inaccessible by car. Just a short walk away is a Princess Cave with decorative spirit house. Free time for sun-bathing, swimming, photography, exploring. ( Not Include National Entrance Fee THB 100, to be pay direct ) 2nd stop Tub Island: An exotic tropical island, ideal for easy snorkeling and exploring on foot. If the tide is low, you can walk along the white sandy causeway joining the neighboring island. 3rd Chicken Island: Natural landmark, named after the shape of its unique limestone rock jutting out into the sea, excellent snorkeling opportunities in warm, inviting waters, rich in coral life. 4th Poda Island: Sunning jewel of the Andaman Sea with both lowland, picturesque bamboo plantation and majestic, rocky cliffs, bordered by long,beautiful beach. Lunch at the beach and break. DAY03 KBV / KUL (B/L) After breakfast, check-out ,then transfer to Krabi City Tour to Wat Thrum Sir , Tiger Cave Temple, Krabi Town Area , Marine Fish Rehabilitation Centre (Royal Family Project) , One - Thambun Province - One Product Centre. After lunch transfer to airport for flight back home with sweet memories. ( Lunch - Duck Noodle, subject to local tour guide arrangement ) Important note : In the event of the early departure or late arrival due to the time constraints, We reserves the right to change and reduce the coverage and sequence of the above itinerary. 第一天 吉隆坡 - 甲米 班机从吉隆坡抵达在甲米国际机场，导游与司机接团后，入进酒店。style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\" lang=\"ZH-CN\"> 第二天 乘搭长尾船游４离岛之旅 （早餐 , 午餐） 早餐享用于酒店后，将有船带您探索 Andaman Sea 如下： 第一站 Pranangstyle=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\" lang=\"ZH-CN\"> 海滩：偏僻海岛 , 步行到公主山洞，观看特别的装饰。自由活动，享受日光浴，游泳和照相。 第二站 Tub 海岛：一个很特别的热浪岛，适合浮潜和徒步探索。在底潮的时候，露出水面的细长的沙滩把两个岛连接起来。 第三站 Chicken 鸡岛：天然和独特的石岩形状，非常棒于浮潜，拥有清溪的水和珊瑚。style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\" lang=\"ZH-CN\"> 第四站 Poda 海岛：位于 Andaman 海上的岛，您可在此享受日光浴，这还有美丽如画的竹子种植场，您还可攀岩。 第三天 甲米 / 吉隆坡minor-latin;\" lang=\"ZH-CN\"> （早餐 , 午餐） 享用早餐于酒店后，进行市区游览参观老虎洞寺庙， 甲米镇海鱼海洋研究及发展中心 & O.T.O 中心 (One-Thambun \" Province\" -Product) 自由活动至时间集合送往机场飞返美丽的家园。 （午餐在地方餐馆享用，mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\" lang=\"ZH-CN\"> 高度推荐地方著名食物有鸭子面条 ） 温馨提醒：由于航班时间的限制，本公司保留权利更改或以上的行程。\";s:9:\"published\";N;s:5:\"state\";i:1;s:6:\"access\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"language\";s:1:\"*\";s:18:\"publish_start_date\";s:19:\"2012-10-29 05:34:05\";s:16:\"publish_end_date\";s:19:\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\";s:10:\"start_date\";s:19:\"2012-10-29 05:34:05\";s:8:\"end_date\";s:19:\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\";s:10:\"list_price\";N;s:10:\"sale_price\";N;s:7:\"type_id\";i:6;}'),(87,'index.php?option=com_k2&view=item&id=123','index.php?option=com_k2&view=item&id=123:chiangmai-free-easy&Itemid=199','Chiang Mai Free & Easy','3D2N CHIANGMAI FREE & EASY 三天两晚 清迈自由行 DAY 01 KUL - CNX Upon arrival, Meet our local representative and proceed tour to visit Sam Kham Village ( Home Industry ) which is well know place themajor traditional handicraft center in Chiangmai. You can see there','2012-11-01 00:43:59','bf6d94cb95ccdec86da571fa34b4be0f',1,1,1,'*','2012-10-29 05:32:33','0000-00-00 00:00:00','2012-10-29 05:32:33','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,6,'O:19:\"FinderIndexerResult\":18:{s:11:\"\0*\0elements\";a:25:{s:2:\"id\";s:3:\"123\";s:5:\"alias\";s:19:\"chiangmai-free-easy\";s:7:\"summary\";s:7447:\"<p class=\"MsoNormal\">3D2N CHIANGMAI FREE &amp; EASY</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">三天两晚</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">清迈自由行</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">DAY 01  KUL - CNX</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Upon arrival, Meet our local representative and proceed tour to visit Sam Kham Village ( Home Industry ) which is well know place themajor traditional handicraft center in Chiangmai. You can see thereal creating for Thai Silk, Cotton Products, Jewelry, Painting work, Umbrella,and Healthy Food Products such as Royal Jelly Bee or Honey, Bird Nest and other. Afterthat, transfer to hotel for check in &amp; rest.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">DAY 02  CNX                                                (B)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">After breakfast at hotel, free at own leisure or join optional tour at own expenses.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">DAY 03  CNX - KUL                                      (B)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">After breakfast, free at own leisure until transfer to international airport for home sweet home.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Important note : In the event of the early departure or late arrival due to the time constraints, We reserves the right to change and reduce the coverage and sequence of the above itinerary. </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">第一天</span>    <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">吉隆坡</span>- <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">清迈</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">抵达机场后，将由我们当地的导游服务并参观</span>Sam Kham<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">村庄</span>(<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">国内产业</span>)<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\" lang=\"ZH-CN\">是清迈主要传统工艺品。您可看到泰国丝绸真正创造、棉花产品、首饰、绘的工作、伞和健康食品：例如蜂蝗浆或蜂蜜，燕窝和其他。在游览以后，送往入住酒店及休息。</